aceholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Incorporations</h4><p>We help sole traders and partnerships transition into limited companies, with advice on liability protection, ownership structure and long-term growth.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Demergers and business splits</h4><p>From separating trading arms to preparing for a sale, we support clients with complex demergers and reorganisations.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Asset and liability separation</h4><p>Protect key assets and ring-fence liabilities through strategic legal structuring, tailored to your commercial goals.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Preparation for sale or investment</h4><p>Restructuring as a first step toward sale or investment? We’ll help you make the right moves now, to save issues later.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Tax-driven restructures</h4><p>We work alongside your tax advisers to make sure the structure is not just legally sound, but tax-efficient too.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Group reorganisations</h4><p>Advice on simplifying group structures or moving entities within a group, to support long-term business planning.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I wanted to take the opportunity and send a big thank you to you, Rebecca and Daisy. I have never before experienced a situation similar to the one I found myself in recently, and I must say having you in my court made all the difference (and I won’t exaggerate if I say it helped me sleep at night).</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I am so pleased that we chose to work with Alex and her colleagues on this project, as they have been an absolute pleasure to deal with and so helpful and patient along the way, making the process much easier than it could have been and getting us to the position we are now in, with a completion! </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I still remember when we first met almost 23 years ago now (come May/June) in your office in Kampala and am therefore delighted that all those years later and after the help you have provided at different points, that you and your colleagues have played such a big part in the sale process to the EOT and completion.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Moonstone Advocates. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">A special mention to Alex Hall who went above and beyond in her assistance to get our deal over the line. In what ended up being very difficult protracted negotiations, Alex made herself available to us throughout and worked evenings and I am sure some weekends to assist us. She is a very valuable asset to the business, and we cannot speak highly enough of.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Recently both Alex Hall and Hayley Blackburn were fantastic, among other members of the team at Moonstone, when we used their services during the sale of our business. Making what was a very stressful process as simple as possible.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I couldn’t recommend Alex Hall enough. Alex gave a very personal service from day one. Nothing was too much trouble for Alex, from giving regular updates on the sale of my business to making sure I fully understood all the legal jargon.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Corporate Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"team-member_item\"><a href=\"/our-people/edward-labeja\" class=\"team-member_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"team-member_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/team/placeholder.svg\" class=\"image is-team\"></div></div><div class=\"team-member_text-wrapper\"><div fs-list-field=\"full-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Edward Labeja</div><div class=\"hidden-text\"><div fs-list-field=\"first-name\">Edward</div><div fs-list-field=\"last-name\" class=\"text-size-